data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Robert Marshall, Director of Family Housing, and U.S. Navy Capt. William Whitmire, Assistant Chief of Staff, Facilities, Marine Corps Installations - West, discuss the Resident Energy Conservation Program during a town hall meeting with Camp Pendleton Residents. The goal of RECP is to promote good stewardship of resources and environment through awareness, personal responsibility, and education.
